        </a>
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div id="applicationsIndex" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwo">
      <div class="panel-body">

        <p>
          Post the access_grant token (from oauth#authorize) together with several other paramers as described below.
          Receive your access_token in the json response
        </p>

        <p>HTTP Request: <code>GET http://api.hackcentral.co/v1/applications</code></p>

        <div id="request">
          <h3>Request:</h3>

          <strong>Route:</strong>
          <p>
            <code>
              GET /v1/applications
            </code>
          </p>

          <strong>Headers:</strong>
            <p>
              <pre>
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer put_access_token_here
Host: api.producthunt.com
              </pre>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div id="response">
          <h3>Response:</h3>

          <strong>Status:</strong>
          <p>
            <pre>200 OK</pre>
          </p>

          <strong>Headers:</strong>
          <p>
            <pre>
X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
X-XSS-Protection: 1; mode=block
X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
Cache-Control: no-store
Pragma: no-cache
Content-Type: application/json; charset=utf-8
            </pre>
          </p>

          <strong>Body:</strong>
          <p>
            <pre>
[
  {
    id: 1
    reimbursement_needed: true
    created_at: "2015-01-01T18:46:35.134Z"
